<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN" 
"http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd" >
<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv='Content-type' content='text/html;charset=UTF-8'>
      <title>Prevent Table Resizing</title>
    </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Prevent Table Resizing</h1>

    <p>The following table will resize on risizing the window:</p>
    <table border="1">
      <tr>
        <th>Column One</th>
        <th>Column Two</th>
        <th>Column Three</th>
        <th>Column Four</th>
        <th>Column Five</th>
        <th>Column Six</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Item 1</td>
        <td>Item 2</td>
        <td>Item 3</td>
        <td>Item 4</td>
        <td>Item 5</td>
        <td>Item 6</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <p>By adding width="600" the following table will not resize on risizing the window:</p>
    <table border="1" width="600">
      <tr>
        <th>Column One</th>
        <th>Column Two</th>
        <th>Column Three</th>
        <th>Column Four</th>
        <th>Column Five</th>
        <th>Column Six</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Item 1</td>
        <td>Item 2</td>
        <td>Item 3</td>
        <td>Item 4</td>
        <td>Item 5</td>
        <td>Item 6</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <p>By surrounding the following table in a fixed width div, it will not resize on resizing the window:</p>
    <div style="width:600px">
      <table border="1">
        <tr>
          <th>Column One</th>
          <th>Column Two</th>
          <th>Column Three</th>
          <th>Column Four</th>
          <th>Column Five</th>
          <th>Column Six</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>Item 1</td>
          <td>Item 2</td>
          <td>Item 3</td>
          <td>Item 4</td>
          <td>Item 5</td>
          <td>Item 6</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>